  <name>Eskerra</name>
  <summary>Desktop companion for your local Eskerra vault — notes, podcasts, and playback</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Eskerra opens a folder-based vault on your machine: markdown in Inbox, podcast notes from General, and MP3 streaming with playlist state.</p>
    <p>On Fedora and GNOME, playback integrates with the shell via MPRIS (media keys and system controls). RSS sync and some mobile-only accelerations are not required for this desktop release; the vault layout stays compatible with the Android app.</p>
  </description>
